value.0: Greetings. Are you in need of assistance <sir/madam>?
And I am a Knight. We are equals in the eyes of the law.
What can I assist you with?
I am a knight of Agis in service to the realm. Is there something else I can assist you with?

*There is a short pause as the Knight contemplates the question.*

No.

Is there something else I can assist you with?

There is a hostel at Fort Briarwood, due west. There is also an inn inside the village of Brost. If you seek ale only, you may simply visit Ale Ye' Below...The soldiers named it.

Hold on a second. Are you just arriving in Brost County?

<StartAction>[The Knight looks over you in an appraising fashion.]</Start>
Have you registered with the County Record Keeper?

<StartAction>[The Knight slowly nods.]</Start>
Then you should make your way to the Village of Brost and find Arkus, but be careful on the road...They say there's a body on the Tejarn Trail to the south. That means the undead are active again. Don't follow the Trail unless you're eager for some bounty coins.
Aye. The Crown pays for proof of deeds against the Undead...Amongst other foul things.
